PRIVACY POLICY

This Privacy Policy describes how MS Software Solutions, LLC (“Company,” “we,” “us,” or “our”) collects, uses, stores, discloses, and otherwise processes personal information in connection with the Flight Star mobile application and any related features, content, and services we provide (collectively, “Flight Star” or the “Services”).

By accessing or using Flight Star, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with this Privacy Policy, do not use the Services.

1. Scope of This Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy applies to personal information we collect or process when you:
•	create an account or sign in to Flight Star,
•	create or manage a user profile,
•	purchase or maintain a subscription through Apple,
•	submit ratings, reviews, comments, favorites, private notes, reports, messages, screenshots, or attachments,
•	interact with AI-powered features,
•	contact support or communicate with admin,
•	or otherwise access or use the Services.

